<p>My setup consists of 6 features. I have feature named "Server". If Server feature is not installed WIXUI_EXITDIALOGOPTIONALCHECKBOX  should be disabled or hidden.</p>  <pre><code>&lt;Publish Dialog="ExitDialog" Control="Finish" Event="DoAction" Value="LaunchApplication"&gt;WIXUI_EXITDIALOGOPTIONALCHECKBOX = 1 AND NOT Installed&lt;/Publish&gt; &lt;Property Id="WixShellExecTarget" Value="[#exefile]" /&gt; &lt;CustomAction Id="LaunchApplication" BinaryKey="WixCA" DllEntry="WixShellExec" Impersonate="yes" /&gt; &lt;Property Id="WIXUI_EXITDIALOGOPTIONALCHECKBOXTEXT" Value="Launch application"/&gt; </code></pre>